# Content generation policy
# Source of truth is hand-authored briefs in `priv/content_plan/**`.
# Only generated docs output under `priv/pages/docs/**` is marked as generated.
# Other `priv/pages/**` content remains human-authored unless explicitly added here.

priv/pages/docs/**/*.md linguist-generated=true
priv/pages/docs/**/*.livemd linguist-generated=true

# Keep plan briefs explicitly human-authored.
priv/content_plan/** -linguist-generated
